WEBVTT

00:07.040 --> 00:09.840
THE TALE OF THE SILKEN ROBE

00:09.920 --> 00:12.280
Sir, we have a new performance,
The Tale of the Silken Robe.

00:12.360 --> 00:14.760
A lost mother, an abandoned child,
and a courtroom trial of the father.

00:14.840 --> 00:16.800
A life adrift, tangled with
love and resentment,

00:16.880 --> 00:18.640
and an unbreakable bond
between a father and a son.

00:18.720 --> 00:19.800
Please step inside.

00:33.000 --> 00:34.160
Please come in.

00:39.800 --> 00:41.320
That young lady in the fox mask,

00:41.400 --> 00:43.600
-keep an eye on her.
-Yes, sir.

00:43.680 --> 00:46.960
Let's see what happens next

00:48.280 --> 00:50.200
The entire family

00:50.280 --> 00:55.120
Was murdered by the bandit, Xu Neng

00:56.280 --> 00:58.240
Xu Neng?

00:59.160 --> 01:02.200
That's my father's name

01:02.280 --> 01:05.200
Could my father be…

01:06.240 --> 01:10.920
Unbelievable!

01:11.000 --> 01:12.360
Bravo!

01:12.880 --> 01:14.960
Nice!

01:16.160 --> 01:17.160
This play is excellent.

01:18.600 --> 01:21.640
But with the son discovering his father
is not only a bandit

01:21.720 --> 01:23.240
but possibly his mother's killer,

01:23.840 --> 01:25.800
I suppose this must end in tragedy.

01:25.880 --> 01:27.360
Please listen on and see for yourself.

01:31.800 --> 01:33.040
Not necessarily.

01:33.720 --> 01:35.320
People love plays because,

01:35.400 --> 01:38.760
no matter how great the conflict,

01:38.840 --> 01:40.160
they often end with reconciliation.

01:40.240 --> 01:43.640
Life, on the other hand,
is far less forgiving.

01:45.840 --> 01:47.160
It's easy to find companions in joy

01:47.240 --> 01:48.360
but rare to find those
who share your sorrows.

01:48.960 --> 01:52.160
Young Lady, if you doubt me,
why not watch the ending together

01:52.680 --> 01:54.400
and see whether it's a tragedy
or a happy ending?

01:55.320 --> 01:56.160
Alright.

01:56.760 --> 01:57.800
Remove this screen.

01:57.880 --> 02:00.560
It'll feel more spacious
with the candlelight and breeze.

02:01.680 --> 02:04.160
-Waiter, remove the screen, please.
-Right away!

02:17.520 --> 02:21.120
STRING OF PEARLS, WONDROUS MELODY

02:21.200 --> 02:23.720
Bravo!

02:24.360 --> 02:25.360
How strange.

02:25.440 --> 02:27.360
It's neither a tragedy nor a happy ending.

02:27.440 --> 02:28.880
Is the play unfinished?

02:28.960 --> 02:31.680
The son is an official,
and the father is a bandit.

02:32.360 --> 02:36.040
Family bonds and justice
stand as irreconcilable opposites,

02:36.640 --> 02:38.440
so naturally, the ending is hard to write.

02:38.520 --> 02:41.760
If the second act really depicted
the son putting his father on trial,

02:42.440 --> 02:44.120
wouldn't that be shocking
and unconventional?

02:44.680 --> 02:47.520
You think a son
shouldn't judge his father?

02:48.040 --> 02:49.760
That familial bonds outweigh justice?

02:51.160 --> 02:54.800
What I mean is,
what's wrong with being unconventional?

02:55.800 --> 02:58.360
Filial piety is essential for a son,
and loyalty is paramount for an official.

02:58.440 --> 03:01.720
It all comes down
to whether he chooses to be a good son

03:01.800 --> 03:03.160
or a good official.

03:04.280 --> 03:05.920
When there's no way to satisfy both,

03:06.480 --> 03:09.160
any choice leads to tragedy.

03:11.000 --> 03:14.000
This protagonist is a pitiable man.

03:15.200 --> 03:18.240
This gentleman must also be torn
between family and justice,

03:18.320 --> 03:19.320
which is why he's so sorrowful.

03:24.480 --> 03:26.440
And if it were up to you
to write the ending?

03:28.320 --> 03:31.400
In the courtroom,
judge as the law requires.

03:32.280 --> 03:34.440
Outside the courtroom,
behind closed doors,

03:34.520 --> 03:35.360
return to being a son.

03:36.040 --> 03:37.760
Set aside grand principles

03:38.720 --> 03:40.600
and offer some gentle words.

03:40.680 --> 03:43.520
If that doesn't work,
then just kneel on a washboard.

03:46.240 --> 03:47.640
Well, that would turn it into a comedy.

03:50.840 --> 03:52.640
Ladies and gentlemen,
you're in for a treat!

03:52.720 --> 03:54.360
In celebration of the Granary Festival,

03:54.440 --> 03:58.920
I've prepared a riddle game
with small prizes

03:59.000 --> 04:01.120
to entertain and delight you.

05:22.600 --> 05:26.320
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

05:29.360 --> 05:32.040
The objects hidden are from the tavern.

05:33.400 --> 05:35.680
The actors will perform clues as hints.

05:36.200 --> 05:37.920
Everyone is welcome to guess.

05:38.560 --> 05:40.360
The one with
the most correct answers wins.

05:43.000 --> 05:45.360
Now, let's begin with the first question!

05:46.560 --> 05:50.000
Empty city walls, galloping warhorses

05:50.600 --> 05:55.800
Year after year
Corpses pile high and crows wail

05:56.320 --> 05:57.480
Warhorses?

05:58.600 --> 05:59.840
That wouldn't fit under the cover!

06:00.440 --> 06:01.720
That's from the Three Tunes of Yuyang.

06:01.800 --> 06:04.320
Mi Heng beat the drum and rebuked Cao Cao.

06:04.840 --> 06:06.000
The object must be drumsticks.

06:07.000 --> 06:07.920
Correct!

06:08.000 --> 06:09.280
Bravo!

06:12.920 --> 06:15.560
You even know about
historical military references?

06:16.080 --> 06:18.720
Could you be a man disguised as a woman?

06:20.560 --> 06:22.320
A woman can be just as capable as any man.

06:29.600 --> 06:31.520
Now for the second riddle!

06:31.600 --> 06:34.720
Surrounded by women's attire

06:34.800 --> 06:36.840
Yet standing tall
As if holding up the sky

06:36.920 --> 06:41.080
Who says it's the domain of men?

06:42.040 --> 06:43.640
Hua Mulan joined the army
in place of her father.

06:44.240 --> 06:46.840
To disguise herself as a man,
she had to wipe away her makeup.

06:46.920 --> 06:50.720
The object in the box
must be rouge used by opera actresses.

06:51.480 --> 06:52.640
Correct!

06:53.360 --> 06:54.280
Bravo!

06:55.720 --> 06:57.960
You're so knowledgeable
about women's cosmetics.

06:58.480 --> 07:00.680
Do you often frequent brothels?

07:00.760 --> 07:02.880
In books, there is beauty to be found.

07:12.160 --> 07:15.080
Hey, why don't the two of you
take your bickering home?

07:15.160 --> 07:16.600
-Spare us all this back-and-forth.
-Right.

07:16.680 --> 07:18.200
-Right, guys?
-Just go home.

07:18.280 --> 07:19.720
-Yes.
-Yes.

07:19.800 --> 07:21.000
What's the fun in that?

07:21.520 --> 07:23.080
It's only interesting if there's a winner!

07:23.160 --> 07:26.920
Exactly. To give up without a fight
would be unworthy of a man.

07:29.800 --> 07:31.800
Is there a third riddle?

07:31.880 --> 07:34.480
-Yes, is there?
-Yeah.

07:35.680 --> 07:37.480
Here comes the third riddle!

07:37.560 --> 07:41.320
Hearing the Song of Chu stirs sorrow

07:41.400 --> 07:45.080
Tears flow as one longs for home

07:45.680 --> 07:47.560
The Battle of Gaixia,
surrounded by the Song of Chu.

07:47.640 --> 07:49.160
-The Chu army…
-The Chu army longs for home.

07:50.480 --> 07:52.560
And longing for home
means a desire to return.

07:54.840 --> 07:57.120
The item must be from the tavern's menu.

07:57.200 --> 07:58.080
Angelica root, which also
symbolizes return home.

08:11.480 --> 08:13.040
-Correct!
-Bravo!

08:13.640 --> 08:15.920
Correct! This young lady
wins by a slight edge.

08:16.000 --> 08:18.440
We both answered, I was just quicker.

08:19.320 --> 08:20.680
Thank you for letting me have this one.

08:20.760 --> 08:22.600
Those two words
you blurted out, "return home,"

08:23.120 --> 08:24.800
are a luxury I dare not hope for.

08:25.600 --> 08:26.840
I concede wholeheartedly.

08:37.520 --> 08:39.960
What do you think is on his mind?

08:40.760 --> 08:42.400
He's upset about losing?

08:45.840 --> 08:49.360
He's thinking about the family
he's at odds with

08:49.440 --> 08:51.880
and the hometown he hasn't
returned to in a long time.

08:54.800 --> 08:55.960
Congratulations, madam.

08:57.520 --> 08:58.520
Thank you.

09:02.920 --> 09:04.480
A painting of
the Twenty-Four Filial Exemplars?

09:05.600 --> 09:08.080
Too bad, it's of no use to me.

09:20.280 --> 09:21.200
Young Master!

09:22.600 --> 09:23.480
Young Master!

09:25.520 --> 09:27.160
My young lady would like you to have this.

09:35.960 --> 09:38.720
I dare to take a guess
at the riddle of your heart.

09:38.800 --> 09:39.880
Though I'm not sure if I'll get it right.

09:41.040 --> 09:42.920
You are knowledgeable and talented,

09:43.000 --> 09:45.440
losing not in wisdom
but to the weight of family sorrow.

09:46.800 --> 09:49.960
If your loved ones are still here,
why not try humbling yourself,

09:50.760 --> 09:53.040
just as in the story of entertaining
one's parents with colorful clothes?

10:07.160 --> 10:10.320
A mask hides her face,
and our meeting was brief.

10:10.920 --> 10:13.120
Yet she is so perceptive and insightful.

10:18.720 --> 10:21.360
Young Master,
Grand General has sent an urgent message.

10:21.440 --> 10:22.720
A typhoon has struck Futing.

10:22.800 --> 10:23.840
Disaster relief requires
your immediate return.

10:29.560 --> 10:31.040
A scented sachet?

10:41.000 --> 10:42.040
That's an item for women.

10:42.840 --> 10:44.280
Were you at…

10:44.360 --> 10:47.080
Don't overthink it.
I went to watch a play.

10:48.120 --> 10:50.520
It must have gotten caught on me while
I was walking alongside other guests.

10:51.320 --> 10:54.240
Given your discreet departure
from the army,

10:54.320 --> 10:55.840
it's best to keep your whereabouts hidden.

10:55.920 --> 10:57.160
You should just discard it.

10:59.080 --> 11:00.200
A lady's belonging

11:00.280 --> 11:02.560
falling into the wrong hands
could cause unnecessary trouble.

11:03.320 --> 11:06.240
I'll return it to her myself
when we meet again.

11:06.840 --> 11:10.800
Oh, and pass this lantern to my father.

11:15.880 --> 11:18.040
I'll see you at the inn an hour later.

11:48.040 --> 11:50.200
Send her home at dawn
once I'm done with her.

11:50.280 --> 11:52.200
Get out of here and lay low for now.

11:52.280 --> 11:53.560
-Yes, sir.
-Go.

12:05.200 --> 12:06.080
Pang Kun Bai?

12:07.920 --> 12:10.040
-What are you trying to do?
-What am I trying to do?

12:10.640 --> 12:12.600
I'm going to enjoy
a good time with you, of course.

12:16.680 --> 12:18.040
How did you…

12:23.440 --> 12:26.800
-How did you…
-Well, let's enjoy a good time then.

12:26.880 --> 12:27.760
Beat him!

12:30.800 --> 12:31.960
Please stop!

12:32.480 --> 12:33.680
Show me mercy!

12:35.120 --> 12:37.960
I came here to stargaze,
but it turned into such a good show.

12:38.480 --> 12:39.640
Interesting.

12:41.760 --> 12:43.040
Please spare us!

12:43.120 --> 12:44.520
We're just hired hands doing a job!

12:44.600 --> 12:47.040
You have the skills but
refuse to use them for good.

12:47.120 --> 12:49.920
Instead, you defile women
and ruin their reputations.

12:50.000 --> 12:50.880
Killing you would be justified.

12:55.880 --> 12:57.800
Dou Zhao, it's a misunderstanding!

12:57.880 --> 12:59.720
I was knocked out
and brought here by them too.

12:59.800 --> 13:01.840
I don't know anything!

13:01.920 --> 13:03.120
Don't hit me! I'll take responsibility!

13:03.200 --> 13:04.960
I'll marry you.

13:05.040 --> 13:07.360
-No one will speak ill of you.
-Shut up!

13:07.440 --> 13:10.000
When I saw you exchanging glances
with Wang Ying Xue at the banquet,

13:10.080 --> 13:12.040
I knew you were up to something.

13:12.760 --> 13:14.200
I had someone look into you.

13:14.280 --> 13:16.040
You're her nephew.

13:16.120 --> 13:20.120
You two bank on the idea that a woman
values her reputation above all else,

13:20.200 --> 13:21.800
thinking the Young Lady would
choose to marry you in the end.

13:22.400 --> 13:24.760
You wanted her private wealth,
which she worked hard for over ten years,

13:24.840 --> 13:26.520
to become her dowry and fill your coffers.

13:26.600 --> 13:29.080
Let's see who's more afraid of the scandal

13:29.600 --> 13:31.280
reaching the authorities,

13:31.360 --> 13:33.760
me or your Wang family,
which would lose its reputation entirely?

13:33.840 --> 13:34.800
Take them away!

13:43.920 --> 13:44.960
Scram!

13:51.600 --> 13:55.480
Little dreamer, looks like Grandmother
has been taking good care of you.

13:55.560 --> 13:59.360
It's a book left by a carefree recluse,
meant for someone destined to find it.

14:00.120 --> 14:02.800
Looks like you're that lucky one.

14:04.960 --> 14:05.880
Yuan Tong?

14:08.320 --> 14:09.200
It really is you.

14:10.240 --> 14:11.360
What are you doing here?

14:11.440 --> 14:12.280
Since you're a friend,

14:12.920 --> 14:14.560
why did you let that scoundrel
Pang Kun Bai go?

14:17.560 --> 14:18.760
You were putting on an act for me.

14:22.240 --> 14:23.600
Aunt!

14:24.120 --> 14:25.120
Aunt!

14:26.720 --> 14:29.680
-What are you…
-Aunt, we're in trouble!

14:29.760 --> 14:31.920
What… What happened to you?

14:33.280 --> 14:35.600
You're a grown man, and you
even brought some men with you.

14:35.680 --> 14:37.400
How did you get beaten up by a girl?

14:38.000 --> 14:40.560
Aunt, she… She knew what we were up to.

14:40.640 --> 14:41.840
We walked right into her trap!

14:41.920 --> 14:43.160
Useless!

14:43.760 --> 14:45.520
Madam! Madam, it's bad!

14:45.600 --> 14:47.000
Young Lady Zhao is here
with the authorities!

14:49.680 --> 14:52.280
Quickly, hide in the side room! Go!

14:57.880 --> 14:58.960
Madam!

14:59.040 --> 15:00.360
Is everything alright here?

15:00.440 --> 15:02.800
I was out admiring the lanterns
and got attacked by bandits.

15:02.880 --> 15:05.920
Together with Constable Wang and his men,
we chased them all the way here.

15:06.000 --> 15:08.520
And turns out
this is my own family's estate!

15:09.400 --> 15:10.720
This is Dou's Residence.

15:11.240 --> 15:12.800
Bandits wouldn't dare to hide here.

15:12.880 --> 15:14.480
What a ridiculous notion.

15:14.560 --> 15:16.560
-Let go of me!
-Constable Wang.

15:16.640 --> 15:18.320
He's here.

15:18.400 --> 15:19.520
You…

15:20.640 --> 15:24.080
How dare you?
These two children are family.

15:24.160 --> 15:26.000
What's this outsider doing here
making baseless accusations?

15:27.200 --> 15:28.720
Madam Wang, a pleasure to meet you.

15:29.240 --> 15:32.440
My name is Ji Yong,
a distant relative of Old Madam Cui.

15:32.520 --> 15:33.640
I'm the one who reported this
to the authorities.

15:33.720 --> 15:35.520
Young Master Ji is the latest
top scorer in the provincial exams.

15:35.600 --> 15:36.600
Take him away!

15:38.240 --> 15:39.280
Let go of me!

15:39.880 --> 15:40.920
Aunt! Aunt!

15:41.680 --> 15:42.920
Help, Aunt!

15:43.000 --> 15:45.000
-Aunt!
-Madam.

15:46.720 --> 15:48.800
It really hurts when you're betrayed
by your family, doesn't it?

15:49.640 --> 15:52.080
Or was it your idea all along?

15:52.160 --> 15:53.360
You…

15:53.440 --> 15:55.640
This is a serious matter, very serious.

15:55.720 --> 15:57.400
I'll go fetch Fifth Master
and Seventh Master

15:57.480 --> 15:58.360
to accompany us to the authorities.

15:58.960 --> 16:01.200
Any misunderstandings
can be cleared up there.

16:03.480 --> 16:04.600
No! They…

16:04.680 --> 16:07.520
They're already asleep.

16:08.040 --> 16:10.200
Let's not trouble them over this, alright?

16:11.960 --> 16:13.000
You put on quite the performance.

16:14.560 --> 16:15.960
If you had taken him
to the authorities yourself,

16:16.040 --> 16:19.920
they wouldn't have dared charge him due
to the Wang and Dou families' influence.

16:21.080 --> 16:22.600
But being arrested by them
is a different story.

16:23.520 --> 16:26.240
Wang Ying Xue will have
a hard enough time explaining this

16:26.760 --> 16:28.280
to my father and the Wang family.

16:29.640 --> 16:31.760
Preposterous! You've gone too far!

16:32.400 --> 16:34.520
He's just a distant nephew.

16:34.600 --> 16:36.640
You'd rather believe him than me?

16:36.720 --> 16:40.160
I can't believe he would accuse me
of something as serious as kidnapping!

16:40.800 --> 16:42.880
Your own nephew turned
against you and accused you,

16:42.960 --> 16:43.800
how can that be false?

16:44.440 --> 16:46.440
I just can't understand.

16:46.520 --> 16:49.000
You used to be
such a kind and patient woman.

16:49.680 --> 16:51.400
Why have you become like this?

16:54.560 --> 16:55.400
Master,

16:56.840 --> 16:59.640
is it me who's changed, or is it you?

17:00.920 --> 17:03.960
No matter how others
mocked me in the past,

17:04.720 --> 17:07.000
you always defended and protected me.

17:07.640 --> 17:09.760
But somewhere along the way,

17:10.800 --> 17:15.040
we ceased to be
just Shi Ying and Ying Xue,

17:15.760 --> 17:17.960
we became merely Master and Madam.

17:18.560 --> 17:22.359
Ever since we slept in different rooms,
you've seen me as a villain.

17:23.000 --> 17:26.040
Anytime something bad happens to Dou Zhao,

17:26.119 --> 17:27.720
you pin the blame on me!

17:32.000 --> 17:34.440
Let's stick to the matter at hand.
Don't bring up unrelated issues.

17:35.080 --> 17:36.520
This isn't unrelated!

17:37.200 --> 17:39.200
I know you've never moved on
from Gu Qiu's death,

17:39.280 --> 17:41.920
and so you blame everything on me.

17:42.640 --> 17:43.800
It's been 16 years.

17:44.760 --> 17:46.640
Has Dou Zhao ever
shown filial respect to you?

17:47.160 --> 17:49.080
But I, Wang Ying Xue,

17:49.880 --> 17:52.680
whether at home or in the court,

17:52.760 --> 17:55.720
have poured everything I have
into supporting your family.

17:56.280 --> 17:57.960
What more do you want from me?

17:58.040 --> 18:00.080
You might as well divorce me!

18:00.760 --> 18:02.600
Ying Xue, Ying Xue!

18:02.680 --> 18:03.960
That's not what I meant.

18:04.040 --> 18:06.240
But Shou Gu has indeed been wronged.

18:06.320 --> 18:07.160
Father.

18:08.400 --> 18:09.360
Mother.

18:12.400 --> 18:15.040
Zhao has ordered for the carriage.
She's leaving.

18:16.440 --> 18:17.440
Ming,

18:18.120 --> 18:20.960
your mother's eyes
are irritated by pollen.

18:21.040 --> 18:22.440
Wipe her tears for her.

18:23.720 --> 18:24.800
Yes, Father.

18:31.560 --> 18:33.080
Mother, you've devoted yourself
to managing the household.

18:33.160 --> 18:36.320
-Father knows this in his heart.
-I know.

18:37.080 --> 18:39.000
But he always takes Dou Zhao's side.

18:39.600 --> 18:41.600
If I didn't cause a scene today,

18:41.680 --> 18:43.840
how else would I remove
this thorn from his heart?

18:43.920 --> 18:46.320
Father longs for family harmony.

18:46.960 --> 18:48.440
Why not be more magnanimous

18:48.520 --> 18:50.720
and try to mend your relationship
with Zhao and Grandmother?

18:50.800 --> 18:52.680
I'm the matron of this house.

18:53.200 --> 18:56.040
Why should I bow to them?
Have you lost your mind?

18:57.640 --> 19:00.400
As long as she stays unmarried,
your marriage can't even be discussed.

19:01.000 --> 19:05.120
Her enormous wealth
should be used as your dowry!

19:05.720 --> 19:09.280
Whether my dowry is more or less,
whether I'm getting married early or late,

19:09.360 --> 19:10.880
I don't care about all of that.

19:10.960 --> 19:12.000
Foolish girl!

19:14.160 --> 19:18.640
I didn't give the Dou family a son,

19:19.720 --> 19:24.000
so I have no choice
but to fight for what's ours.

19:24.080 --> 19:28.440
But I never expected
you to grow into such a spineless coward.

19:28.960 --> 19:31.760
Now I don't even know what
I've been fighting for all this time.

19:32.760 --> 19:33.880
If I knew you'd be like this,

19:34.560 --> 19:38.000
I never would have
let someone else raise you!

19:39.480 --> 19:40.440
Mother,

19:41.200 --> 19:42.280
I know I'm useless,

19:42.360 --> 19:46.160
but I really don't want you
taking such great risks for me.

19:47.960 --> 19:49.960
Loan-sharking is
explicitly forbidden by the court.

19:50.040 --> 19:53.240
Over the years, you've been
working with the Cangbei Gang…

19:53.320 --> 19:54.280
Silence!

19:54.960 --> 19:57.720
You mustn't speak of such things.

20:00.080 --> 20:00.920
You're crying?

20:01.000 --> 20:03.480
All you ever do is cry.
What good does crying do?

20:03.560 --> 20:07.240
I know that, but I just can't help it.

20:08.520 --> 20:09.960
I'm so useless.

20:13.840 --> 20:14.720
Ming,

20:14.800 --> 20:16.560
since you know crying is useless,

20:16.640 --> 20:18.520
you must do everything I say.

20:19.800 --> 20:20.680
Remember,

20:20.760 --> 20:24.520
your dowry, your family's influence,
and your reputation

20:24.600 --> 20:26.560
will all affect your marriage prospects.

20:27.440 --> 20:29.440
If I don't fight for you today,

20:29.520 --> 20:33.000
your future will be nothing
but a life of walking on eggshells.

20:34.360 --> 20:36.400
You can't even control your tears now.

20:36.920 --> 20:41.240
How will you ever endure
the hardships of being a wife?

20:45.200 --> 20:46.280
Shou Gu.

20:49.080 --> 20:52.000
Shou Gu, I failed to protect you.

20:52.520 --> 20:54.240
This is all my fault.

20:54.760 --> 20:56.480
I promise I'll make it up to you.

20:57.280 --> 20:58.680
It's not your fault, Father.

20:59.880 --> 21:02.080
It's mine for ever having expectations
in the first place.

22:01.920 --> 22:02.960
Done.

22:03.480 --> 22:05.680
Peony Fish Fillet,
a famous dish of Sichuan.

22:05.760 --> 22:08.160
The preparation for
Peony Fish Fillet is so intricate.

22:08.240 --> 22:10.160
Even restaurants
in the capital rarely serve it.

22:10.240 --> 22:11.800
Shou Gu, who taught you how to make this?

22:13.600 --> 22:14.600
Let me try a bite first.

22:14.680 --> 22:18.000
Zhang Ru, I made this for Ji Jian Ming.

22:18.080 --> 22:19.440
It wouldn't be proper
for you to eat it first.

22:20.320 --> 22:21.200
Alright then.

22:21.280 --> 22:23.480
I'm not sure if he likes spicy food,

22:24.000 --> 22:26.440
so I also made him
Thousand Threads Shrimp.

22:27.360 --> 22:28.760
Zhang Ru, what are you doing?

22:28.840 --> 22:30.960
Su Su, what have you been
busy with over there?

22:33.080 --> 22:35.600
I wanted something auspicious,
so I made a dessert.

22:35.680 --> 22:37.520
Gold and Jade Treasure.

22:39.480 --> 22:40.880
It looks great.

22:40.960 --> 22:42.880
I wonder what he's thinking.

22:42.960 --> 22:45.200
He gives up the comforts of the capital

22:45.280 --> 22:46.640
and insists on staying
in this countryside estate.

22:46.720 --> 22:50.120
Yes, Zhao, tell us how you two met.

22:51.320 --> 22:56.200
I met him when I was little,
at the Wanfo Temple.

22:58.120 --> 22:59.320
Given your condition…

22:59.840 --> 23:02.760
You might as well
just return to heaven instead.

23:05.040 --> 23:06.200
Go.

23:06.280 --> 23:09.400
Within misfortune lies fortune,
you two are bound by fate.

23:10.040 --> 23:11.840
The course of destiny
is now in your hands.

23:13.720 --> 23:15.720
With Young Master Ji's ethereal looks,

23:15.800 --> 23:17.600
becoming a monk would be such a waste.

23:17.680 --> 23:20.000
I wonder if he'd be willing
to become a live-in son-in-law.

23:21.040 --> 23:23.400
Zhao, how far have things
progressed between you two?

23:23.480 --> 23:25.800
I haven't seen him in ages.

23:25.880 --> 23:27.400
And yet you're making
Peony Fish Fillet for him.

23:27.480 --> 23:29.000
-You've never made it for me.
-That's right.

23:29.080 --> 23:30.400
I'll make it for you next time.

23:30.480 --> 23:33.400
Young Lady Zhao, Old Madam
is having migraines again.

23:36.440 --> 23:38.600
Doctor, how is Grandmother's condition?

23:39.840 --> 23:42.040
Her migraines are a result of years of
accumulated stress. It can't be rushed.

23:42.120 --> 23:44.840
Just follow the prescription,
and she'll recover gradually.

23:45.560 --> 23:47.240
-Thank you, Doctor.
-I'll take my leave now.

23:49.800 --> 23:50.920
Quack!

23:52.040 --> 23:53.520
-Who are you calling a quack?
-Whoever is answering me.

23:53.600 --> 23:55.680
-You…
-Quack! Quack! Quack!

23:55.760 --> 23:58.600
I won't argue with a brat like you!
Good day!

24:22.720 --> 24:25.000
If you're going to follow
that quack's prescription,

24:25.080 --> 24:26.520
not even the gods can save her.

24:26.600 --> 24:27.880
Don't jinx her!

24:28.480 --> 24:30.520
Oh? And do kind words save lives?

24:35.120 --> 24:36.360
Take off Old Madam's clothes.

24:40.800 --> 24:41.720
You can save her, right?

24:43.520 --> 24:44.840
The root of her illness is blocked energy,

24:44.920 --> 24:46.520
stuck in the Zhongwan
and Taichong acupoints.

24:46.600 --> 24:48.880
One above the navel,
the other on the top of the foot.

24:48.960 --> 24:50.320
Her clothes must be removed
for proper needle therapy.

24:50.920 --> 24:51.920
You're a man, after all.

24:52.000 --> 24:53.880
Shouldn't we find a female doctor instead?

24:53.960 --> 24:55.560
Female doctors are scarce to begin with.

24:56.560 --> 24:58.400
Grandmother hasn't eaten
or drunk anything.

24:58.920 --> 24:59.760
There's no time to delay.

25:04.680 --> 25:05.800
Grandmother.

25:05.880 --> 25:07.840
Everyone has their fate.

25:09.200 --> 25:11.520
Perhaps my time has come.

25:12.480 --> 25:13.840
This is unbelievable.

25:13.920 --> 25:16.360
It's a treatable illness,
yet you refuse to treat it.

25:16.440 --> 25:18.840
If everyone clings to propriety
and rules, what's the point of doctors?

25:18.920 --> 25:23.320
Old Madam, isn't your life more important
than some outdated proprieties?

25:25.080 --> 25:25.920
Grandmother,

25:26.000 --> 25:28.760
to a doctor, there's no distinction
between men and women,

25:28.840 --> 25:30.040
only patients.

25:30.840 --> 25:34.120
I don't want to lose you
because of societal conventions.

25:34.200 --> 25:37.720
For my sake, please just give it a try.

25:38.520 --> 25:39.560
Grandmother.

25:47.640 --> 25:48.640
Shou Gu!

25:49.160 --> 25:50.600
Shou Gu!

25:51.640 --> 25:53.000
Grandmother finally took her medicine.

25:53.080 --> 25:55.280
-I'll go serve her some plain porridge.
-Go on.

25:55.360 --> 25:56.960
Avoid meat and stimulating food.

25:57.040 --> 25:57.960
Got it.

25:59.760 --> 26:02.040
-Thank you.
-It's nothing.

26:14.000 --> 26:15.240
Thank you.

26:16.000 --> 26:17.320
Grandmother has finally fallen asleep.

26:17.920 --> 26:20.120
Momentary peace doesn't
guarantee lasting health.

26:20.640 --> 26:23.560
Her illness stems from emotional
stagnation and unresolved worries.

26:24.160 --> 26:25.880
If the root cause isn't addressed,
she won't live long.

26:29.600 --> 26:32.840
Grandmother has always
carried a heavy burden in her heart.

26:34.120 --> 26:37.080
She refuses to talk about it,
and I don't know how to help.

26:37.920 --> 26:40.400
If she doesn't want to resolve it,
that's her choice.

26:40.480 --> 26:41.800
Everyone dies.

26:41.880 --> 26:43.560
Just spend more time with her
while she's still here.

26:45.960 --> 26:47.240
That glare you just gave me,

26:47.320 --> 26:49.400
you think I'm heartless
and cruel, don't you?

26:51.720 --> 26:55.520
I just don't understand
why you treat life and death so casually.

27:01.560 --> 27:03.560
My father said I was born
with a closed heart,

27:03.640 --> 27:04.640
indifferent to feelings.

27:04.720 --> 27:07.400
I've never shed a single tear
since I was little.

27:07.480 --> 27:10.320
When I was four, he fell gravely ill.

27:11.040 --> 27:15.600
He gave me this telescope
and told me he would become a star.

27:15.680 --> 27:17.840
So, every night I used it
to watch the stars.

27:17.920 --> 27:19.960
I even learned astronomy by heart.

27:20.800 --> 27:22.040
But I knew,

27:23.160 --> 27:24.360
I wouldn't find him,

27:25.200 --> 27:28.200
because when people die,
they just turn to dust.

27:28.800 --> 27:29.960
Everyone dies.

27:30.880 --> 27:34.120
Living is but a path to death,
and death is the beginning of life anew.

27:34.200 --> 27:35.320
That's right.

27:36.720 --> 27:38.680
What matters is how we live our lives.

27:39.280 --> 27:40.240
So, little dreamer,

27:41.320 --> 27:42.480
how do you want to live?

27:46.360 --> 27:48.080
Honestly, I haven't thought that far.

27:48.960 --> 27:52.280
To live a single lifetime
is already hard enough.

27:53.920 --> 27:55.200
To live it well,

27:57.640 --> 27:59.080
that's a luxury.

28:00.360 --> 28:03.360
If I can spare some energy
to help those around me,

28:03.920 --> 28:05.000
that's more than enough.

28:05.080 --> 28:07.160
You're content with such a simple wish?

28:09.200 --> 28:11.480
What about you? Have you given up
on becoming a monk?

28:11.560 --> 28:14.400
I was only sent to the temple as a child
because of my poor health.

28:15.200 --> 28:17.000
While there, I learned medicine
from the abbot.

28:17.080 --> 28:19.720
A small doctor heals the sick,
a great doctor heals the nation.

28:19.800 --> 28:21.400
I want to become Grand Secretary.

28:21.480 --> 28:22.880
That would be interesting.

28:23.720 --> 28:26.440
I've studied the biographies of grand
secretaries from the past 300 years.

28:26.520 --> 28:28.320
It's a path of gradual
promotions and endurance.

28:28.400 --> 28:31.080
Most of them took at least 50 years
to reach the second rank.

28:31.160 --> 28:32.960
Too slow and not worth it.

28:33.040 --> 28:34.560
I need to find another way.

28:35.920 --> 28:37.920
There's no shortcut
to becoming Grand Secretary,

28:38.640 --> 28:41.640
unless you want to be
a sycophant or a traitor.

28:41.720 --> 28:43.040
That's an option too.

28:46.000 --> 28:47.480
Talking to you is always so fun.

28:48.000 --> 28:49.680
Let's talk more
when I return from the capital

28:50.200 --> 28:51.320
as the top scorer in the imperial exam.

28:53.880 --> 28:57.360
Before you leave for the capital,
I have a favor to ask.

28:59.600 --> 29:01.360
I want to learn medicine from you.

29:02.720 --> 29:06.560
Even though people are destined
to part ways eventually,

29:07.080 --> 29:10.360
I want to do my best
to prolong the time we have together.

29:14.960 --> 29:18.440
THE TRUE TRADITION OF MEDICINE

29:32.320 --> 29:33.520
Not bad.

29:33.600 --> 29:35.640
Young Master Ji and Shou Gu
meet in private every day.

29:35.720 --> 29:37.240
They must be in love. Want to bet on it?

29:37.840 --> 29:39.280
Bring it on.

29:42.280 --> 29:43.640
A chicken and a duck.

29:43.720 --> 29:45.040
What a perfect match.

29:48.840 --> 29:49.760
Let's do it.

29:56.320 --> 29:58.120
Your dissection
of the hen today was decent,

29:58.200 --> 29:59.920
but we'll have to try on
a human body next.

30:00.000 --> 30:01.920
We're going to the mass grave tonight.

30:02.000 --> 30:02.960
All right.

30:03.600 --> 30:05.600
They're going on a date in the mass grave?

30:06.880 --> 30:07.760
You win.

30:08.280 --> 30:10.040
THE TRUE TRADITION OF MEDICINE

30:17.720 --> 30:19.720
Ji Yong? Ji Yong?

30:20.520 --> 30:22.440
Ji Yong? Ji Yong?

30:24.960 --> 30:27.320
I invited Ji Jian Ming here

30:27.840 --> 30:30.120
just to see if he and Shou Gu
might be a good match.

30:30.840 --> 30:32.400
You're so perceptive.

30:32.480 --> 30:34.360
Look how well they suit each other!

30:35.440 --> 30:37.600
One doesn't know how to love,
and the other isn't interested in it,

30:37.680 --> 30:39.160
they do make a fitting pair.

30:41.360 --> 30:45.600
Too bad it's never going to work out.

30:46.800 --> 30:47.840
Study the medical texts regularly.

30:47.920 --> 30:49.880
If I find out you've been
slacking off when I return,

30:49.960 --> 30:51.880
-you'll be in for some needles.
-Fine.

30:52.400 --> 30:54.160
But if you fail the exam,
you'll also be in for needles.

30:55.480 --> 30:57.600
But failing the exam would be too easy.

30:57.680 --> 31:00.000
If I don't top the exam,
I'll let you do whatever you want.

31:03.960 --> 31:05.480
The nation is suffering
from deep-rooted problems,

31:05.560 --> 31:07.120
and I've diagnosed it.

31:08.160 --> 31:11.480
I've heard the higher the rank,
the harder it is to retire.

31:13.200 --> 31:16.040
Becoming a historically renowned
statesman isn't necessarily fun.

31:16.120 --> 31:17.600
Local officials' laziness
is just a symptom,

31:17.680 --> 31:19.760
systemic flaws in administrative
structures are the root cause.

31:19.840 --> 31:22.200
If reforms are enforced from the
top down, streamlining and discipline

31:22.280 --> 31:23.480
could save countless taels

31:23.560 --> 31:25.640
and restore vitality to the nation.

31:26.160 --> 31:27.040
I'm off.

31:33.200 --> 31:36.320
He is extraordinarily gifted
and ambitious.

31:36.400 --> 31:39.800
But why did he shave his head
and became a monk in my dreams?

31:40.400 --> 31:41.840
Amitabha.

31:42.360 --> 31:43.200
JI YONG, PRODIGIOUS MONK

31:43.280 --> 31:45.240
A prodigy to rival Wenchang

31:45.760 --> 31:47.800
Daring to teach Confucius the stars

31:47.880 --> 31:48.720
A LONE MINISTER GAZES UPON THE COLD SEA,
TEN YEARS OF STEADFAST LOYALTY…

31:48.800 --> 31:51.240
Loyalty and treachery, gratitude
And enmity, all dismissed with a smile

31:51.760 --> 31:55.200
The green bamboo and yellow blossoms
Mark the end of the mortal form

31:59.440 --> 32:03.560
FUTING

32:21.880 --> 32:27.800
The Grand Preceptor has
Instructed me to explain the reasoning

32:27.880 --> 32:31.120
The Duke of Ding is in Futing now
for disaster relief.

32:31.200 --> 32:33.120
Our government is out of grain.

32:33.960 --> 32:37.600
We'd better keep a low profile and
avoid drinking banquets these days.

32:38.160 --> 32:39.080
What's there to be afraid of?

32:39.160 --> 32:40.000
GUESTS FEEL AT HOME

32:40.080 --> 32:43.400
You don't understand.
That Song Mo is like a living Yama.

32:43.480 --> 32:46.320
I've heard that once he locks
onto someone and questions them,

32:46.400 --> 32:48.080
-Did you take bribes or not?
-he'll uncover crimes without fail.

32:48.160 --> 32:50.560
-No, I didn't.
-Whether it's imperial relatives,

32:50.640 --> 32:51.960
wealthy merchants,
or high-ranking officials,

32:52.040 --> 32:53.400
he investigates them all the same.

32:58.160 --> 33:00.440
Song Mo, how dare you raid
our Tang family!

33:00.520 --> 33:02.000
Do you even know who my brother is?

33:04.200 --> 33:05.400
Do you know who I am?

33:05.480 --> 33:07.840
The eight Tang brothers control
all the salt affairs, stone mines,

33:07.920 --> 33:09.280
and canal transport in Futing.

33:09.360 --> 33:11.160
Our family won't let you
get away with this!

33:22.000 --> 33:22.920
Who else?

33:29.920 --> 33:31.800
This is disrespectful!
Go back to your stage!

33:32.440 --> 33:34.560
How dare an actor like you
jump on our table!

33:34.640 --> 33:35.680
DING

33:36.520 --> 33:37.640
The Duke of Ding's Army?

33:45.240 --> 33:46.360
General Song?

33:51.160 --> 33:52.760
General Song!

33:52.840 --> 33:54.880
-General Song, spare me!
-General Song!

33:54.960 --> 33:57.320
I'll give you half of my money.
Just let me live!

33:57.400 --> 33:58.360
Alright.

33:59.120 --> 34:02.440
I'll leave you with
half your limbs and organs too.

34:05.480 --> 34:06.480
General, have mercy!

34:06.560 --> 34:08.719
All the embezzled money is here.

34:11.520 --> 34:13.040
Enough to leave you a whole corpse.

34:14.920 --> 34:16.320
If you don't want to die, tell me

34:16.920 --> 34:20.360
where you're hiding
the private grain reserves.

34:26.719 --> 34:28.040
Your Grace, please reconsider.

34:28.679 --> 34:32.040
It's His Majesty's decree to let the
crown prince oversee disaster relief.

34:32.120 --> 34:33.360
While your intentions are good,

34:33.440 --> 34:34.760
speaking against an imperial order…

34:34.840 --> 34:35.679
DING WEI

34:35.760 --> 34:38.000
…is something I dare not do.

34:38.080 --> 34:39.360
Eunuch Ding,

34:41.080 --> 34:44.360
tens of thousands of people are dying.

34:44.440 --> 34:45.760
They can't afford to wait

34:45.840 --> 34:48.600
for a royal to travel thousands
of miles here just to put on a show?

34:49.520 --> 34:52.000
Do they even know how many
people starve to death every day?

34:52.760 --> 34:56.760
I've opened the granaries
for disaster relief on my own.

34:57.560 --> 34:58.840
-Your Grace…
-Relay my words as I said them!

35:00.320 --> 35:02.280
If there are consequences, I'll bear them.

35:03.720 --> 35:04.760
Grand General.

35:05.680 --> 35:07.040
The General has bought grain
from the neighboring county

35:07.120 --> 35:08.200
with confiscated embezzled funds.

35:08.280 --> 35:09.880
The grain is being sent
to the porridge stations.

35:13.120 --> 35:14.280
Well done!

35:14.360 --> 35:15.760
SPRING TREES AND EVENING CLOUDS

35:15.840 --> 35:17.240
I have to go take a look.

35:17.320 --> 35:19.240
-Old Madam.
-Let me go take a look.

35:19.320 --> 35:21.080
-It's fine.
-The rain is too heavy. You can't.

35:21.160 --> 35:22.720
-Grandmother.
-Shou Gu.

35:22.800 --> 35:25.240
Your health has just started to improve.
You shouldn't be out in the rain.

35:25.320 --> 35:26.520
I have to check it myself.

35:26.600 --> 35:28.560
With such heavy rain,

35:28.640 --> 35:30.120
though we've prepared grain

35:30.200 --> 35:32.440
-and repaired the foundations and roofs,
-Hurry!

35:32.520 --> 35:35.440
how can they withstand such a deluge?

35:35.520 --> 35:38.400
The ordinary thatched houses
will collapse.

35:38.480 --> 35:40.800
The tenant farmers
will be left homeless and starving.

35:40.880 --> 35:42.400
-Here.
-Don't worry, Grandmother.

35:42.480 --> 35:44.360
I'm going to work with
the farmers and craftsmen

35:44.440 --> 35:46.120
to repair the canals and distribute food.

35:46.200 --> 35:47.800
I promise to keep the villagers safe.

35:48.400 --> 35:51.080
You should stay here at the estate
and allocate the supplies.

35:51.680 --> 35:53.720
Tuo Niang, stay with Grandmother
and assist her with the arrangements.

35:53.800 --> 35:55.000
Leave the rest to me.

35:55.080 --> 35:57.120
-Then…
-Don't worry, Young Lady Zhao.

35:57.200 --> 35:59.880
You have to be careful, Shou Gu.

35:59.960 --> 36:01.240
Don't worry. I will.

36:03.680 --> 36:05.120
Stay safe!

36:06.880 --> 36:09.600
Don't push! One at a time.
Don't crowd. Step back!

36:09.680 --> 36:11.160
-Line up! There's enough for all of you!
-I'm starving!

36:11.240 --> 36:12.080
CORRUPTED THIEF

36:12.160 --> 36:14.840
-One by one. Hold it still.
-I want one.

36:14.920 --> 36:15.960
Next!

36:16.480 --> 36:18.600
-You will all get some.
-Give me some.

36:18.680 --> 36:21.280
-One by one.
-I'm here first!

36:23.160 --> 36:24.280
Mister,

36:24.800 --> 36:28.640
why is this hairpin made of white stone?

36:28.720 --> 36:32.120
Isn't it heavy to wear a stone
on your head?

36:35.960 --> 36:36.800
Look.

36:39.920 --> 36:41.440
It's not heavy anymore.

36:41.960 --> 36:44.360
No matter what it's for, it can be
exchanged for 30 catties of rice.

36:44.440 --> 36:48.160
Now you and your parents won't go hungry.
Take it.

36:49.840 --> 36:51.080
Thank you, mister!

36:53.200 --> 36:54.560
The grain carts are here!

36:54.640 --> 36:56.320
The grain carts are here!

36:56.400 --> 36:58.000
-Careful.
-Hurry!

36:58.080 --> 36:59.120
Careful!

37:13.760 --> 37:15.080
Watch out!

37:26.560 --> 37:28.320
-Young Lady?
-What's wrong, Young Lady?

37:34.720 --> 37:35.560
-General?
-Mister!

37:35.640 --> 37:37.280
-General?
-General?

37:38.160 --> 37:40.720
-General?
-General!

37:41.240 --> 37:42.840
-General!
-Mister!

38:00.440 --> 38:01.480
Who are you?

38:03.080 --> 38:04.960
Why are you here?

38:09.640 --> 38:10.720
It's you.

38:16.360 --> 38:18.040
We haven't found each other yet.

38:18.880 --> 38:20.200
You cannot die now.

38:43.440 --> 38:44.320
The General is awake.

38:44.400 --> 38:45.360
-He's awake.
-The General's awake.

38:45.440 --> 38:46.280
-He's awake.
-Good.

38:46.360 --> 38:47.800
Thank goodness.

38:48.400 --> 38:49.760
I'll inform the Grand General.

38:51.640 --> 38:52.920
General.

38:53.000 --> 38:56.600
You injured your head three days ago.

38:57.120 --> 38:59.120
We tried everything,
decoctions, acupuncture,

38:59.200 --> 39:01.040
but you just wouldn't wake up.

39:01.120 --> 39:04.320
Fortunately, Grand General saw
this item and decided to ignite it.

39:04.400 --> 39:06.520
Amazingly, it actually worked.

39:24.600 --> 39:26.400
Doctor, what incense is this?

39:26.480 --> 39:27.760
It's benzoin incense.

39:27.840 --> 39:30.000
Legend has it that
after Yang Guifei's death,

39:30.080 --> 39:32.920
Emperor Xuanzong was unable to sleep.

39:33.000 --> 39:34.480
Only this incense could help him sleep

39:34.560 --> 39:36.240
and dream of his lost love.

39:36.840 --> 39:39.520
Oh, I know! The General must have
dreamed of his sweetheart!

39:39.600 --> 39:40.840
Shut up.

39:45.000 --> 39:46.640
She saved my life.

39:49.640 --> 39:50.480
Where's Grand General?

39:51.080 --> 39:53.320
The Grand General stayed
by your bedside all night.

39:53.400 --> 39:55.960
He went to inspect the newly
repaired seawall before dawn.

39:57.480 --> 39:59.240
The weather this year has been strange.

39:59.320 --> 40:00.320
Heavy rains have fallen in many places.

40:00.400 --> 40:03.520
Even Jinmenwei and Zhending
have been affected by disasters.

40:06.080 --> 40:07.360
Zhending…

40:13.880 --> 40:16.560
-There's more.
-Here, have some.

40:17.880 --> 40:19.560
Excuse me.

40:19.640 --> 40:20.560
-Here.
-Thank you.

40:20.640 --> 40:21.680
Thank you.

40:25.080 --> 40:27.760
-Have a bun.
-Thank you.

40:30.520 --> 40:32.240
-Thank you.
-Eat up.

40:32.320 --> 40:34.560
-Thank you.
-Have a bun.

40:35.080 --> 40:37.080
-Here.
-Thank you.

40:38.480 --> 40:39.520
How is it?

40:44.920 --> 40:45.960
Here.

40:46.960 --> 40:47.840
-Distribute it to them.
-Okay.

40:55.720 --> 40:56.960
Thank you.

40:57.040 --> 40:58.440
Don't worry, he'll get better.

41:01.040 --> 41:03.360
SILENCE

41:28.440 --> 41:31.120
TWO WEEKS LATER

41:41.400 --> 41:42.440
Pardon our intrusion.

41:42.520 --> 41:45.000
My master's surname is Mei,
a merchant from the south.

41:45.720 --> 41:47.600
We humbly request lodging for the night.

42:02.160 --> 42:03.000
Young Lady, you're awake.

42:04.280 --> 42:05.240
What time is it?

42:06.080 --> 42:07.040
Just past the third quarter
of the Yin hour.

42:10.440 --> 42:13.960
Young Lady, a group of merchants arrived
at the estate seeking lodging.

42:14.560 --> 42:16.480
Their leader calls himself
Young Master Mei.

42:16.560 --> 42:20.600
But these men have calloused palms
and move silently.

42:20.680 --> 42:23.800
Mr. Chen has sent people several
times asking if you're awake yet.

42:26.040 --> 42:27.640
Invite Mr. Chen over now.

42:43.520 --> 42:44.600
They've surrounded exits of the estate.

42:44.680 --> 42:46.080
They're going to slaughter everyone.

42:46.160 --> 42:48.240
We only took the baby to
ask for a chance of negotiation.

42:48.320 --> 42:51.680
Whether it ends in bloodshed
or discussion is up to you.

42:51.760 --> 42:53.680
Young Lady Zhao,
you're not involved in politics.

42:53.760 --> 42:56.640
How do you know so much about
the Duke of Ding's case?

42:57.160 --> 42:59.160
Who are you, really?

44:48.120 --> 44:49.240
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM.

44:49.320 --> 44:50.800
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA
ARE FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
